divs: Sighting DetailsI am personally not a witness to this, but someone needed to make a report here. For the past week, many residents and motorists have been claiming sightings of UFOs over Irvington, AL at night. This morning, the story was picked up and sensationalized by a local radio station (97.5 WABD) after photos started surfacing of the UFOs themselves. They were boomerang-shaped and emitting light that was described as either green, orange, or white. I have attached a digital image of the purported UFOs. There are apparently other images as well.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Irvington

Summary: A Week of UFO Sightings in Irvington, AL
